'''Valgrind'''是一款用于内存调试、[[内存泄漏|内存泄漏]]检测以及[[性能分析|性能分析]]的[[软件开发工具|软件开发工具]]。Valgrind这个名字取自[[北欧神话|北欧神话]]中[[英灵殿|英灵殿]]的入口。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.valgrind.org/docs/manual/faq.html#faq.whence |title=Valgrind FAQ |access-date=2009-02-10 |archive-date=2021-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330051633/https://www.valgrind.org/docs/manual/faq.html#faq.whence }}</ref>

Valgrind的最初作者是Julian Seward，他于2006年由于在开发Valgrind上的工作获得了第二届[[Google|Google]]-[[O'Reilly_Media|O'Reilly]][[开放源代码|开放源代码]]奖。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://valgrind.org/gallery/awards.html |title=valgrind.org's list of awards |access-date=2009-02-11 |archive-date=2021-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210626153433/https://valgrind.org/gallery/awards.html }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://code.google.com/events/osa-hall-of-fame.html |title=Google-O'Reilly Open Source Awards - Hall of Fame |accessdate=2009-02-11 |archive-date=2008-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080907172740/http://code.google.com/events/osa-hall-of-fame.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

Valgrind遵守[[GNU通用公共许可证|GNU通用公共许可证]]条款，是一款[[自由软件|自由软件]]。

