== 支持平台 ==
到3.3.0版本为止，Valgrind支持[[x86|x86]]、[[x86-64|x86-64]]、[[ARM架構|Arm]]v7以及[[PowerPC|PowerPC]]上的[[Linux|Linux]]。除此之外，还有一些其它非正式支持的类Unix平台（如[[FreeBSD|FreeBSD]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rabson.org/#valgrind |title=Valgrind FreeBSD port |accessdate=2009-02-11 |archive-date=2008-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081023210220/http://www.rabson.org/#valgrind |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[NetBSD|NetBSD]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://vg4nbsd.berlios.de/ |title=Valgrind NetBSD port |accessdate=2009-02-11 |archive-date=2006-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060209063503/http://vg4nbsd.berlios.de/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 以及[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sealiesoftware.com/valgrind/ |title=Valgrind Mac OS X port |access-date=2009-02-11 |archive-date=2021-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210618171923/http://sealiesoftware.com/valgrind/ }}</ref>）。

